                    "item_type": "markdown", 
                    "text": "### Table Legends\n\nThe placeholder `table` legend type is a placeholder no more. Selecting `table` as the legend type for any chart will render a summation table as the legend. "
                  }
                ]
              }, 
              {
                "item_id": "d28", 
